  16 Nov 2010; Hakan Demiralp <keenblade@tuxfamily.org>
  jack-audio-connection-kit-1.9.6.ebuild:
  jack-audio-connection-kit: fixed alsa support. wrt #106 by nilekurt.

*jack-audio-connection-kit-1.9.6 (14 Nov 2010)

